><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Tarife Kontenjanının Dağıtımı<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Dağıtım yöntemi aşağıdaki şekilde uygulanacaktır:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Talep Toplama<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Başvurular öncelikle <b>talep toplama yöntemi</b> ile\r\ndeğerlendirilecektir.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Talep miktarı kontenjanı aşmıyorsa talepler tamamen\r\nkarşılanacaktır.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Talep kontenjanı aşarsa Bakanlık;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">başvuru tarihi, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">talep miktarı, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">fiili sarfiyat, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">üretim miktarı, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">üretim kapasitesi, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">tüketim kapasitesi, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">geçmiş ithalat\r\nmiktarı, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">önceki kontenjan\r\nkullanım performansı <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">gibi kriterlerden bir veya birkaçını dikkate alarak\r\ntahsis gerçekleştirecektir.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">İlk Gelen İlk Alır<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Talep toplama sonrasında kontenjan kalması halinde;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">kalan miktar <b>ilk\r\ngelen ilk alır</b> yöntemiyle dağıtılacaktır. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Tek bir ithal\r\nlisansına verilecek miktar, kalan kontenjanın <b>%10'unu geçemeyecektir.</b> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Aynı firmaya yeni\r\nithal lisansı düzenlenebilmesi için son ithal lisansının düzenlenme tarihinden\r\nitibaren <b>en az 15 gün</b> geçmiş olması gerekecektir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">İthal Lisansının Kullanımı<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Tarife kontenjanı kapsamında ithalat yapılabilmesi için;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Ticaret Bakanlığı\r\ntarafından düzenlenen <b>ithal lisansının</b> bulunması zorunludur. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Lisans elektronik\r\nortamda (Tek Pencere Sistemi) düzenlenecektir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Firmaya ayrıca\r\nyazılı belge gönderilmeyecek, yalnızca e-posta ile <b>23 haneli TPS belge\r\nnumarası</b> bildirilecektir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Beyannamenin <b>44\r\nno.lu kutusunda</b> belge referans numarası ve belge tarihi beyan edilecektir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">İthal Lisansı Geçerlilik Süresi<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Düzenlenecek ithal lisansları;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">15 Şubat 2027 (dahil)</span></b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">\r\ntarihine kadar geçerli olacaktır.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Devir ve Revize<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">İthal lisansları <b>üçüncü\r\nkişilere devredilemez.</b> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Bakanlık gerekli\r\ngördüğü hallerde lisansı resen revize edebilir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Firma talebiyle\r\nrevize yapılabilmekle birlikte <b>lisans miktarının artırılmasına yönelik\r\ntalepler kabul edilmeyecektir.</b> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Bakanlığın Yetkileri<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Ticaret Bakanlığı;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">başvurulardaki bilgi\r\nve belgeleri incelemeye, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">ilave belge\r\nistemeye, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">ithal lisanslarını\r\niptal etmeye, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">gerekli görülen\r\nhallerde inceleme yapmaya veya yaptırmaya <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">yetkili olacaktır.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Yürürlük<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Tebliğ, <b>yayımı tarihinde yürürlüğe girmiştir.</b><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\">Kaynak: <a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/07/20260701-12.htm\">https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/07/20260701-12.htm</a><o:p></o:p></p>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"\">\n                                    \n                                </a>"}
